# --- The fence around the workshop ------------------------------------
# Raw source material, kept out of the history: Raw_Assets/ is the human
# inbox (Nicolai drops raw art in Grafik/, sound in Lyde/, tracks in
# Music/) and the mills in tools/ read from here and write game-ready
# files into assets/. It is 1.9 GB and nothing raw may enter the repo.
#
# Anchored with a leading slash on purpose: without it these match at any
# depth, and a bare "Music/" pattern would swallow assets/music/ as well.
/Raw_Assets/

# Node lives here for the mills only; the game does not ship it.
node_modules/
.expo/

# Generated tuning pages -- rebuilt by the build:eq and build:rain mills,
# and they embed the audio and the ground, so versioning them is pointless.
tools/eq-preview.html
tools/rain-preview.html

# Recordings are mill intermediates: regenerable from the harness pages.
/tools/recordings/

# Local-only archive: never in git; the tracked arkiv/ entries are enough.
/arkiv/lokalt/
